<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">终风</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson20f791f840dd">
终风且暴，顾我则笑，谑浪笑敖，中心是悼。<br />终风且霾，惠然肯来，莫往莫来，悠悠我思。<br />终风且曀，不日有曀，寤言不寐，愿言则嚏。<br />曀曀其阴，虺虺其雷，寤言不寐，愿言则怀。
</div>
</div>
